## Neo4j Brand Colors

Reference: https://neo4j.design/40a8cff71/p/606e3d-brand-colors

### Primary Colors

| Color Name | Hex Code | Usage |
|------------|----------|-------|
| **Mid Baltic** | `#014063` | Primary brand blue - use for main elements |
| **Lime** | `#00CC52` | Neo4j green - use for accents and success states |
| **White** | `#FFFFFF` | Backgrounds and text on dark backgrounds |

### Secondary Colors

| Color Name | Hex Code | Usage |
|------------|----------|-------|
| **Slate** | `#485662` | Body text and secondary elements |
| **Light Gray** | `#F5F7FA` | Page backgrounds |
| **Teal** | `#006E58` | Active states and secondary accents |
| **Link Blue** | `#0056B3` | Links and interactive elements |
| **Hover Blue** | `#25459E` | Link hover states |
| **Light Teal** | `#E7FAFB` | Light backgrounds and highlights |

